Regression Prediction Problem

- distance between the y value of the prediction and observation is the ERROR in our prediction
RMSPE: sqrt((1/total # of predictions)* 
            ((y value of observation point 1 - y value of predicted point 1)^2 +
            (y value of observation point 2 - y value of predicted point 2)^2 +
            ...
            (y value of observation point n - y value of predicted point n)^2))
RMSE: same formulla except on the data used to train the model







